author: Brenda Goh
title: Three negatives and a positive: problems with coronavirus tests in China
description: Trader He Ximing in the Chinese city of Wuhan says he has no idea how or where he caught the coronavirus or why repeated nucleic acid tests showed he didn't have it.
content:
WUHAN, China (Reuters) - Trader He Ximing in the Chinese city of Wuhan says he has no idea how or where he caught the coronavirus or why repeated nucleic acid tests showed he didn’t have it.
